{"tid":889033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司徒華民主運動　其下商業部門　營業額年逾 億元","createTime":"2018-11-04T08:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T04:32:01.000Z","uid":47714,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3f21773e1c9cc0e032e8ba7c34f026d117e6046d","tid":889033,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T08:55:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkptu.org/ptunews/479/share.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkptu.org%2Fptunews%2F479%2Fshare.htm&d=wzQ11qHcU%2B4SXBjieBAQhAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=27e36339\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkptu.org/ptunews/479/share.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n司徒華先生高瞻遠矚，深諳獨立生存之道，明白掌握穩健而充裕財源，才能發揮力量。不然的話，資源緊絀，不容易在各方面長期堅持，一則往往後繼乏力而受制於政府的勢大財雄，二則或會因為接受財閥或政團資助而喪失獨立自主的原則。<br />\n<br />\n司徒華先生曾以農業、輕工業和重工業比喻。這是從整體規劃考慮，先鞏固經濟根基，才能健康成長和壯大，繼而進一步發展各項工作。解決日常生計所需，免得仰人鼻息，處處求助於人，這是基本生存要義，因此，必須好好處理生財大計！<br />\n<br />\n無疑教協營運有術，也得到廣大會員的支持，業務不斷穩定發展，從超級市場到牙醫服務，從視光中心到醫療化驗所，從教協田園圖書坊到翠明假期，職員達八十餘人，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>每年營業額逾億港元</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/news/art/20110103/14828643\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20110103%2F14828643&d=wzQ11qHcU%2B4SXBjieBAQhAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=95f69234\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20110103%2F14828643&h=6744d2f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/news/art/20110103/14828643</a><br />\n<br />\n教協會務蒸蒸日上，全憑老先生精明治會。他說：「教協成功之道，在能把農業、輕工業和重工業都辦得好。」農業是指教師的職業保障，有飯吃是先決條件；輕工業是指教協的營商事務，包括超級市場和其他業務的營運，以取得經濟獨立，治會不受外權干預；重工業指社會事務，爭取公義和平民主，教協責不旁貸。"},{"pid":"155f769858bb91c460cd7f89d2f8bbc54ad4544a","tid":889033,"uid":61280,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:11:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蚑徒華！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"67a15ebaef67568b72cd662a460ed23a3cf1ae3f","tid":889033,"uid":141151,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"每年營業額逾億港元<br />\n賺幾多先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會淨係夠養住班staff"},{"pid":"6ca1e3c308df1e14829fab3c4cb9709ee7ab4b7a","tid":889033,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"67a15ebaef67568b72cd662a460ed23a3cf1ae3f","tid":889033,"uid":141151,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"每年營業額逾億港元<br />\n賺幾多先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會淨係夠養住班staff"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:16:59.000Z","msg":"應該唔會負數<br />\n重點係佢想顯佢資金調動可以上億 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b39f70519e831f4450bf8bb4024d47c4bcb148e","tid":889033,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:18:13.000Z","msg":"好多咩 &lrm;寶蓮禪寺一年都多過你"},{"pid":"7a6aeb5e329aca4dfdbfce51a369ef208bb2a7c3","tid":889033,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:02:31.000Z","msg":"網台課金咪仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db1686837b26e0452f826419b0eac60f9df57c4","tid":889033,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:15:21.000Z","msg":"超級市場成日賣支那貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd54d2bf23a76a1482e326a480586402f069005c","tid":889033,"uid":13724,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:23:28.0